{"tid":54388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姓賴的？批餐飲油煙已成霧霾的源頭","createTime":"2016-12-25T13:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T01:06:45.000Z","uid":22736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a07cdf7987c6cd1f4fc1811aa2c35c056919f7","tid":54388,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161225&amp;guid=56091669&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161225%26guid%3D56091669%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=BYkiD%2BDBrvhqhOaPkH73qBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=f9e9a8b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161225%26guid%3D56091669%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=4544a440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161225&amp;guid=56091669&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n內地霧霾情況越來越嚴重，不但令到民眾透不過氣，更讓多個地方有人想舉行抗議，中共喉舌《人民日報》今日刊文，將矛頭指向各地餐飲業的油煙。<br />\n<br />\n文章稱，幾十座城市在霧霾前要工廠停產、汽車限行，但仍阻不了空氣重污染，認為餐飲的油煙令到霧霾出現。<br />\n<br />\n文章更引述之前的測試，稱炒一碟辣椒便能讓PM2.5爆錶，而北京的空氣中13% PM2.5，都是來自餐飲油煙，油煙問題已「不是人們想象的芝麻綠豆了」。<br />\n<br />\n對於官媒的說法，不少網民都怒批說法荒謬：「感覺自己的智商受到了侮辱！」「這種自欺欺人的宣傳現在還能糊弄誰？」「說實話，污染佔大頭的誰都知道！」「這年頭吃個飯都是錯&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/25/212340_70c57fa2cfcc9d99995cf385b8101744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F25%2F212340_70c57fa2cfcc9d99995cf385b8101744.jpg&h=4b9e033b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c4c430a718c200fe6a06137089808428d8bdd7c","tid":54388,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"立法規定以後只准吃生肉"},{"pid":"9dcec1a8ed0f9562d1abf81e732b3740693eb708","tid":54388,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"